Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.08,0:00:19.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.02,0:00:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 这是什么情况
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.83,0:00:29.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是经常在漫画里看到的 秀恩爱情侣经常做的秀恩爱行为
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.85,0:00:30.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这算什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.81,0:00:31.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一点也高兴不起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.89,0:00:32.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.42,0:00:33.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说有点吓人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.26,0:00:37.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 阿良良木君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.57,0:00:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「啊」呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.56,0:00:41.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.10,0:00:53.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能见到你的笑容我真的是很高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.56,0:00:57.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿良良木君 脸上粘了饭粒
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.94,0:00:59.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你粘上去的
